<br>
Firstly, I failed to mention that this is an aging dragon.  A bit senile.  A dragon who keeps inventories to make sure his hoard is all there... and, well, a dragon who wants to make sure everything turns out all right when he dies.  So, he is doing this job for his god, essentially (if it's a deep dragon, it could be Lloth, otherwise Tiamat is always a good choice.  Details).  He needs to find this specific rare magical item.  This idea of summoning people is how he decided to do it, at least to start.  I'll make sure that each PC has an item of a similiar type to make that work out better, as well.<br>
