<br>
If the dragon has secretly accepted the Cult's offer, if you killed the dragon it would only make the dragon be able to become a dracoliche that much sooner...<br>
<br>
If you were to take the item with you or were to try to destroy the item, the dragon would likely accept the Cult's offer to become a dracoliche and remain upon the world, in lieu of life immortal...<br>
<br>
If you allow the dragon to use the item, the dragon becomes immortal...<br>
<br>
